headline: Orbital Biocarbon secures key investment to grow biosolids solution
summary: The funding round led by Toby Z. Rice, a seed investor in Archaea Energy, allows Orbital to pursue more contracts in the Northeast, where disposal capacity is tight and concerns about PFAS contamination are growing.
